    "title": "Ushauri kutoka kwa Wengine",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "ushauri kutoka kwa wengine",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kitabu cha Mithali kinafundisha kwamba kuwa na washauri wengi ni jambo jema kwa sababu wanatoa usalama (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:14\">Mithali 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:6\">24:6</a>). Wanaboresha nafasi zetu za mafanikio (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:22\">Mithali 15:22</a>). Kitabu cha Ayubu kinaonyesha kwamba washauri wanaweza pia kupotosha, hata kama kile wanachoamini kuhusu Mungu kinaonekana kuwa sahihi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:17\">Ayubu 12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:3\">26:3</a>).</p><p>Hapo mwanzo, marafiki wa Ayubu walijiunga naye katika mateso yake, wakikaa kimya kwa huzuni kwa siku saba (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11-Job2:13\">Ayubu 2:11–13</a>). Hata hivyo, faraja yao ilikoma walipoanza kuzungumza. Marafiki wa Ayubu mara nyingi walizungumzia wazo la kibiblia la kupanda na kuvuna, ambalo ni sehemu muhimu ya agano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1-Lev26:46\">Mambo ya Walawi 26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:31\">Mithali 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:8\">22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:7\">Hosea 8:7</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7-Gal6:8\">Wagalatia 6:7–8</a>). Hatuwezi kupuuza maneno yao kwa sababu mengi ya yale waliyosema ni mafundisho sahihi kuhusu asili ya Mungu na jinsi anavyotenda kuelekea wanadamu.</p><p>Hata hivyo, marafiki wa Ayubu walitumia vibaya wazo hili (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:8\">Ayubu 4:8</a>). Hawakuchunguza maisha ya Ayubu ili kubaini alikosea wapi na kisha kumwonya kuhusu hukumu ya kiungu. Badala yake, walipuuza maisha ya uaminifu ya Ayubu na kuzingatia mateso yake. Kisha wakadhani alikuwa anateseka kwa sababu ya dhambi. Hatimaye, Mungu aliwaita washauri hawa waongo. Hii inatukumbusha kwamba lazima tutumie kwa usahihi ukweli kuhusu Mungu ili kumfurahisha Mungu na kusaidia wengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2-Prov15:4\">Mithali 15:2–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:23\">23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">Isaiah 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29\">Waefeso 4:29</a>).</p><p>Ni muhimu kuzingatia ushauri kutoka kwa vyanzo mbalimbali. Hata hivyo, tunapaswa kuulinganisha na kile tunachoamini kuwa ni sahihi mbele za Mungu (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22\">Matendo 20:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:4\">21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:11\">11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">13</a>). Mungu anaweza kutumia washauri wa kibinadamu kutusaidia kuelewa mapenzi yake. Lakini pia anatuelekeza kupitia Roho wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:15\">Yohana 16:13–15</a>).</p><p>Yesu Kristo ni “Mshauri wa Ajabu” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">Isaya 9:6</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:29\">Isaya 28:29</a>). Ana “hazina zote za hekima na maarifa” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:3\">Wakolosai 2:3</a>). Tunapowasaidia wengine wakati wa huzuni, tunapaswa kuwa waangalifu na wenye kufikiri tunapotumia mafundisho kutoka kwa Maandiko. Mara nyingi, uwepo wetu wa kimya ndio msaada muhimu zaidi tunaoweza kutoa.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:1-2Sam17:23\">2 Samweli 17:1–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:3-1Kgs12:17\">1 Wafalme 12:3–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:15-1Kgs22:28\">22:15–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:9-Job2:10\">Ayubu 2:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:8\">4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:17\">12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:2\">16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:5\">Mithali 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:9\">9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:14\">11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2-Prov15:4\">15:2–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:22-Prov15:23\">22–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:20\">19:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:18\">20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:6\">24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">27:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">Isaya 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:29\">28:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14\">Warumi 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29\">Waefeso 4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:3\">Wakolosai 2:3</a></p>",
